text: Abdou Mbacke Thiam (born 3 February 1992) is a Senegalese footballer who plays as a forward for Louisville City FC in the USL Championship. ==References== ==External links== *Profile at UCONN Athletics Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Louisville City FC players Category:USL Championship players Category:Senegalese footballers Category:Senegalese expatriate footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:UConn Huskies men's soccer players Category:Senegalese expatriate sportspeople in the United States Category:Expatriate soccer players in the United States Category:Sportspeople from Dakar
